data.description: Space Space Space...2 story gem offering amazing space with endless possibilities. The block is dreamy and quiet. Two door entryway certainly makes an impression. A fabulous fireplace to help give this home unique character. This home also offers two car garage with a storage area. Did I mention you also have attic space? Minutes away from restaurants and shops on Main St. You will enjoy the experience of the newly approved revitalization of Main St in Kings Park. Must see first hand to appreciate everything this wonderful home can offer.
